                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "生命流束"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素伤害</span>，抓1张<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">唤醒眷属</span>，生成2层<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">绿洲之滋养</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/7abf617a4cbf7dfd0d8af8ea344109a0_2897522401911206581.png",
                "id": "talent36828",
                "key": "终景迸落",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "终景迸落"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，生成6张<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">唤醒眷属</span>，随机放入牌库。我方召唤4个<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">增殖生命体</span>后，此角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">重燃的绿洲之心</span>，并获得2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">护盾</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/78668ff054322fa748bbe935edb4a58e_5057985980075394601.png",
                "id": "talent85990",
                "key": "增殖感召",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "增殖感召"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">事件牌</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">打出此牌或舍弃此牌时：</span>召唤一个独立的增殖生命体。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7648313714347928319.png",
                "id": "talent71882",
                "key": "唤醒眷属",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/278323e83f9dfa38fbdac8e74932cb1b_3753346009878338229.png",
                "title": "唤醒眷属"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7607123506426474797.png",
                "id": "talent5624",
                "key": "增殖生命体",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/278323e83f9dfa38fbdac8e74932cb1b_5261304067318767010.png",
                "title": "增殖生命体"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着草元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火元素伤害的[<span style=\"color: white\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: white\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_6761975384209668799.png",
                "id": "talent27101",
                "key": "草元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">绿洲之滋养</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方打出唤醒眷属时：</span>少花费1个元素骰。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>（可叠加到3）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重燃的绿洲之心</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>所附属角色造成的伤害+3。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色使用技能后：</span>移除我方场上的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">绿洲之滋养</span>，每移除1层就治疗所附属角色1点。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">舍弃</span></strong></p><p>通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_451345948854468426.png",
